title: Good to Go! Market
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Natural and bulk food grocery market with a prepared foods deli that offers also vegan, gluten free, dairy free, and vegetarian food. Has seitan, dairy-free cheese, gluten free bread, salad, and 2 soups each day. Has seating, free Wi-Fi.
